{"sn43.44:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 43.44 ","sn43.44:0.2":"2. Dutiyavagga ","sn43.44:0.3":"Parayanasutta ","sn43.44:1.1":"“Parayananca vo, bhikkhave, desessami parayanagaminca maggam. ","sn43.44:1.2":"Tam sunatha. ","sn43.44:1.3":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, parayanam? ","sn43.44:1.4":"Yo, bhikkhave, ragakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—","sn43.44:1.5":"idam vuccati, bhikkhave, parayanam. ","sn43.44:1.6":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, parayanagami maggo? ","sn43.44:1.7":"Kayagatasati. ","sn43.44:1.8":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, parayanagamimaggo. ","sn43.44:1.9":"Iti kho, bhikkhave, desitam vo maya parayanam, desito parayanagamimaggo. ","sn43.44:1.10":"Yam, bhikkhave, satthara karaniyam savakanam hitesina anukampakena anukampam upadaya, katam vo tam maya. ","sn43.44:1.11":"Etani, bhikkhave, rukkhamulani, etani sunnagarani. Jhayatha, bhikkhave, ma pamadattha; ma paccha vippatisarino ahuvattha. Ayam vo amhakam anusasani”ti. ","sn43.44:1.12":"(Yatha asankhatam tatha vittharetabbam.) ","sn43.44:1.13":"Tettimsatimam. ","sn43.44:1.14":"Dutiyo vaggo. ","sn43.44:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn43.44:2.1":"Asankhatam anatam anasavam, ","sn43.44:2.2":"Saccanca param nipunam sududdasam; ","sn43.44:2.3":"Ajajjaram dhuvam apalokitam, ","sn43.44:2.4":"Anidassanam nippapanca santam. ","sn43.44:3.1":"Amatam panitanca sivanca khemam, ","sn43.44:3.2":"Tanhakkhayo acchariyanca abbhutam; ","sn43.44:3.3":"Anitikam anitikadhammam, ","sn43.44:3.4":"Nibbanametam sugatena desitam. ","sn43.44:4.1":"Abyabajjho virago ca, ","sn43.44:4.2":"suddhi mutti analayo; ","sn43.44:4.3":"Dipo lenanca tananca, ","sn43.44:4.4":"sarananca parayananti. ","sn43.44:4.5":"Asankhatasamyuttam samattam. "}